      <h2>Campaigns Listing</h2>
      <p>Playground customers are usually managing multiple ad campaigns at once, each containing multiple ad creatives and audience targetting.</p>
      <p>My challenge: to provide users with immediate insight into the performance of their campaigns on login.</p>
      <p>I drafted and iterated on layout concepts for the application in Balsamiq Mockups, then coded up concepts with HTML/CSS/JS to create a data-driven, moving prototype.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-cell grid8 single-image">
      <img src="/images/reporting/dashboard1.jpg" alt="" style="align-self: flex-end">
    </div>
  </section>

